description: Classically styled, gold plated cufflinks bearing a curving design on the oval face, with a subtly hammered surface completing the air of artisan craftsmanship. These cufflinks combine the best elements of old and new styling and manufacture to complete a gentleman’s attire in an enduring and understated fashion.
